<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>도덕 수업: 토론 마스터의 길 (Large)</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700;800&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #f0f4f8; font-size: 1.125rem; }
        .card-hover:hover { transform: translateY(-8px); transition: all 0.3s ease; }
        .gradient-text { background: linear-gradient(45deg, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
        .floating { animation: floating 3s ease-in-out infinite; }
        @keyframes floating {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
        }
        /* 가독성을 위해 자간 및 행간 조정 */
        p { line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-900">

    <header class="bg-white border-b-2 border-slate-200 sticky top-0 z-50 shadow-md">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8 py-6 flex justify-between items-center">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-4xl">⚖️</span>
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-black tracking-tight text-slate-900">오늘의 도덕 수업</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold border border-blue-200">1학년 1학기</span>
                <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold border border-purple-200">자유학기제 기록ing</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8 py-12">
        
        <section class="mb-16 text-center">
            <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 rounded-full text-lg font-black mb-6 border border-indigo-200 shadow-sm">📢 필독! 수업 안내</div>
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-6 leading-tight">토론 카드로 <span class="gradient-text">논리 근육</span> 키우기!</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-2xl font-medium">오늘은 실전 토론을 준비하는 '트레이닝 데이'입니다.</p>
        </section>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-lg border-2 border-slate-100 card-hover">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-4">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-green-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl shadow-inner">📝</div>
                    <h3 class="font-black text-2xl text-slate-800">진짜 토론하기</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg mb-6 font-medium leading-relaxed">친구들과 직접 논리를 주고받는 시간</p>
                <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-2xl text-sm font-black shadow-md uppercase tracking-wider">수행평가 반영 O</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-lg border-2 border-slate-100 card-hover">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-4">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-orange-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl shadow-inner">🃏</div>
                    <h3 class="font-black text-2xl text-slate-800">토론 카드 활동</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg mb-6 font-medium leading-relaxed">토론 준비 및 구조도 만들기 연습</p>
                <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-slate-500 text-white rounded-2xl text-sm font-black shadow-md uppercase tracking-wider">수행평가 반영 X</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <section class="mb-16">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-black mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="w-2 h-10 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></span>
                오늘의 미션 : 본인의 상태를 선택하세요
            </h3>

            <div class="space-y-6">
                <!-- Group A: Master -->
                <div class="group bg-white border-4 border-transparent hover:border-blue-500 p-8 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-xl transition-all cursor-pointer overflow-hidden relative active:scale-95">
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-6 relative z-10">
                        <div class="flex-1">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                                <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-lg font-black uppercase tracking-widest">MASTER LEVEL</span>
                                <h4 class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-800">[토론 제작자] 학생들</h4>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-slate-500 text-xl font-bold">지난 수업에 이어 '구조도' 단계로 넘어갑니다.</p>
                            <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                                <span class="bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold">#토론카드완성</span>
                                <span class="bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold">#반박_재반박</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-left md:text-right bg-blue-50 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-blue-100 w-full md:w-auto">
                            <span class="text-lg font-black text-blue-700 block mb-1">과제명: 토론 제작자 되기</span>
                            <div class="text-sm text-blue-500 font-bold">구조 설계 및 상세 반박문 작성</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Group B: New Start -->
                <div class="group bg-white border-4 border-transparent hover:border-emerald-500 p-8 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-xl transition-all cursor-pointer overflow-hidden relative active:scale-95">
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-6 relative z-10">
                        <div class="flex-1">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                                <span class="bg-emerald-500 text-white text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-lg font-black uppercase tracking-widest">NEW START</span>
                                <h4 class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-800">오늘 [크롬북 처음]인 친구들</h4>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-slate-500 text-xl font-bold">주제를 정하고 실제 사례를 수집해 봅시다.</p>
                            <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                                <span class="bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold">#핵심질문만들기</span>
                                <span class="bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold">#실제사례조사</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-left md:text-right bg-emerald-50 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 w-full md:w-auto">
                            <span class="text-lg font-black text-emerald-700 block mb-1">과제명: 토론 카드 만들기</span>
                            <div class="text-sm text-emerald-500 font-bold">주제 선정 및 근거 자료 수집</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-indigo-700 rounded-[3rem] p-10 md:p-14 text-white relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
            <div class="relative z-10">
                <h3 class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4 opacity-80 underline underline-offset-8 decoration-indigo-400">COMING NEXT WEEK</h3>
                <h4 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-8 leading-tight">하브루타 모둠별 토론 🤝</h4>
                <p class="text-indigo-100 text-xl md:text-2xl mb-10 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                    오늘 정성껏 만든 카드는 다음 시간의 <span class="text-white font-black underline decoration-yellow-400 decoration-4">강력한 무기</span>가 됩니다!<br>
                    활동 결과를 바탕으로 <span class="bg-white text-indigo-900 px-3 py-1 rounded-xl font-black mx-1">수행평가 토론 모둠</span>이 구성됩니다.
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-lg md:text-xl font-black">
                    <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full animate-ping"></div>
                    오늘의 모든 활동 데이터는 생기부에 소중히 기록됩니다!
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute right-10 bottom-[-10px] text-[10rem] floating opacity-20 select-none">🚀</div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <footer class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8 pb-20">
        <div class="bg-slate-200 h-1 w-full mb-12 rounded-full"></div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-8 text-center">
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-xl font-bold">지금 바로 구글 클래스룸에 입장하여 미션을 확인하세요!</p>
            <button onclick="window.open('https://classroom.google.com')" class="bg-black text-white px-12 py-5 rounded-[2rem] text-2xl font-black hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 shadow-2xl shadow-black/30 group">
                구글 클래스룸으로 이동하기 <span class="inline-block group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">↗</span>
            </button>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        document.querySelectorAll('.group').forEach(card => {
            card.addEventListener('click', () => {
                const title = card.querySelector('h4').innerText;
                // 클릭 시 피드백 애니메이션
                card.style.transform = 'scale(0.98)';
                setTimeout(() => {
                    card.style.transform = '';
                }, 100);
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
